yle=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb1dac47-fd1a-4695-a17c-50d08fc58279\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bf3b6eab-a517-4bad-9e97-9b82e90cadbe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>프랜차이즈 매장에 붙이는 포스터 사양은?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e26a0fad-fb54-4936-90d1-e8a768369f2c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9f0cdb7e-4d38-410e-b496-22c60ceaa557\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a8df8c7-d38a-4867-810c-e0b8e6c8ad4d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-84ab00f9-d3cb-4f62-b79a-44e172d76d8d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-576d2544-97ff-4be6-812e-bf25e8f3d405\" style=\"color:#555555;\">아트지/스노우지 180g 백색</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b2aa0273-ab49-4eb6-8e50-b30d6f25925e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f1482815-ae27-489e-9c1e-9b6c74dba470\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-212834b6-9f83-4427-908f-e850504bd425\" style=\"color:#555555;\">510mm × 740mm ( +- 2~3mm 차이 있음)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d0855b9-98ed-438a-a58f-0b85dc7ac742\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5a09f0e8-c294-49f2-bdd5-5cae1b2e08ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70291141-ca77-4668-a166-626b10ca5c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 기본은 단면 (하지만 요즘은 유리창 양면으로 제작이 가능합니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34dfd1ee-0cf2-489a-8cdf-ba58797dce77\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-868afe14-2d6f-462b-920b-079fd05f55c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d88db466-1072-4daa-8c4a-840ad7b952c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 양면 유광/무광 코팅이 기본입니다. (다만 포스터를 자주 교체하는 프랜차이즈 회사는 코팅처리를 하지 않습니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16ffb48c-2959-4a74-b6e5-466d00d43924\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ffddee07-cfd7-4d92-8032-1cb5260bd0c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b70987d-2f2d-4ea8-b55d-7109f8272950\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 기본 100장 미만 (매장별 개별 발송도 가능합니다. 다만 별도 포장비와 택배 비용이 추가됩니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a638a1a3-6bfe-430c-94e5-8982a7aa7d7b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f24f722f-5d49-4d08-b2de-1836d6bcb6cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-020e8ff0-56b0-4213-8242-301468e1f3bd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-020e8ff0-56b0-4213-8242-301468e1f3bd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MTFfMTA2/MDAxNzQ2OTI4MDI2NDA0.o0z