WfLmOdnnBoQWNP3JMtBIg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b0ed16a-dba7-41dd-bd4e-e0fadc5df304\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7684465e-d23f-4896-882c-7b6dd06784c0\" style=\"\">브랜드 캐릭터</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-84425c96-1909-4f54-8d7c-227eca363435\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0dc8b62-6166-4092-ad64-d1bc485c24a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2498392b-6c9f-4df0-bac0-23cb5a4df7d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이와 같이 브랜드에 관한 CI/BI/Logo/캐릭터 등의 유무는 매우 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-182003d0-24cf-45c2-aeaa-dcaec82e48a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97128119-7bbb-46a0-a959-7b07a85754a0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7b94e15-b336-46d0-aa8f-fb750716f13e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75ff6844-e055-43ed-ba4c-1ba7c3950dc1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-29a1abda-80eb-45d8-a789-1e21a75a72fa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4f7fb4a2-d293-4c8d-975d-33395f07392c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 포스터에 들어가는 사진 이미지는 있습니까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a5070fc5-28f6-48f5-a591-7b0d3955c479\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b4ce7ca7-b227-4c59-8e5b-a78a92f2523f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12496dd6-b3b0-49af-8f5a-f76530db6f68\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53cc7124-dd63-4dc4-9fd7-0268759521c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포스터에는 사진 이미지나 제품 이미지가 필수입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d23a7f29-75a2-49df-a6b8-af891ab13225\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:717px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d23a7f29-75a2-49df-a6b8-af891ab13225\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MTFfMTA2/MDAxNzQ2OTI4ODYxNjY5.BoMZ1KgZJkXiyuM5KBfk3DwjSa_Ep2NHW1zJdVTTzl0g.yvJNYaELpSu7rLW7GjMmrS_LEwl54po0SabgiOLAcgEg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"717\", \"originalHeight\" : \"566\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA1MTFfMTA2/MDAxNzQ2OTI4ODYxNjY5.BoMZ1KgZJkXiyuM5KBfk3DwjSa_Ep2NHW1zJdVTTzl0g.yvJNYaELpSu7rLW7GjMmrS_LEwl54po0SabgiOLAcgEg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-494ff8c1-6f14-4d1f-b5f4-241116cf7f69\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-973977cd-b0f7-427b-872a-af97353bd3a4\" style=\"\">음식 이미지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4f74eee7-3e16-4dbd-9698-cffe85c9a3a5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ccbfa83-de11-4b13-b507-fb8652d2f3a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bf029286-94b3-4220-ab3d-be30f8a06b27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포스터의 생명은 제품이나 음식 사진입니다. 이 사진이 맛나 보이게 또는 있어 보이게 촬영하는 것은 브랜드를 알리는데 매우 중요한 요소입니다. 보정도 필요하고 세팅이나 연출도 매우 중요합니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 협력업체와의 연계로 브랜드에 맞는 제품 촬영을 지원하여 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43715220-d9d3-453e-a659-017955464014\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8aa1c0f-0256-4dce-8cd6-8fe11de8dfa4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92baa8a6-8848-4bf1-93e5-9c312dbceb47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d8a77e07-19dd-4df1-95a9-07a4e3bc8b6e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fe276a9-a892-4bf3-a8b1-3d6d23492e55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3d5b8945-024a-4e67-9df8-fdaa6ea4a6bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>□ 기획비 / 디자인비</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b9f138b-f688-4da0-a234-a637149da5c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-42a60358-1009-495f-8048-7334cf385917\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d8a1f41-5255-4f71-b459-d2d3fb66043d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0ec9dae2-21cc-49e2-bba1-bb26353a9696\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포스터의 기본 요소가 결정되면 기획에 따른 디자인 비용이 책정됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5af2b727-13f3-458b-9443-6e1bfc8cf270\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e8529dd-0369-4213-9bed-3407e0786c61\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통상의 경우 30만원에서 부터 시작합니다. 물론 작업 기간이나 요구사항의 시안 개수 또는 자료의 제공 등에 따라 금액은 매우 유동적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92f26675-050c-403a-b2e0-c296ab3a0a4e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-33b94746-6ad9-4c5a-9fe1-b65011a5e128\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-dae55296-4b12-47a9-9a9f-32abfa3e88eb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f740f41-72c8-433b-829a-73aaf3bc03af\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-678dcd51-2ede-4c42-b8e2-0e9eba353d88\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8493716c-d40f-4394-9edd-f928d33bc7af\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">디자인이 끝나면 생산에 돌입합니다. 위의 사양에 따라 기간은 1일에서 3일 정도 소요됩니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 밸리데이션 체크와 고객과의 소통을 통해 가장 퀄리티 높고 빠르게 진행하여 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-62022a72-959c-4d6d-8ba3-5cef7d7293d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1158a94-5df7-4111-b8b6-a7ee907d833e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223861829773#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
